  "introduced_at": "2023-01-31",
  "number": "646",
  "official_title": "To amend the Internal Revenue Code of 1986 to remove short-barreled rifles, short-barreled shotguns, and certain other weapons from the definition of firearms for purposes of the National Firearms Act, and for other purposes.",
